name: ( Dance Me ) to the End of Love
description:
Dance me to your beauty with a burning violin
Dance me through the panic till I'm gathered safely in
Lift me like an olive branch and be my homeward dove
Dance me to the end of love
Dance me to the end of love
...

( L.Cohen )

I don't really want to comment on this photo, I find it more interesting if everyone can see what they need.

It's always a 400Tmax abused by me ( +3/4 ). Pentax Mx with a SMC 50mm f/1,4.  
Don't remember the speed, I like to play with the 15, so it's probably not above that. The light comes from the moon through a window quite far behind me.

Since I do some NFT, I try to find in digital what I like to do in bi-chromated gum or in Van-Dyke for example. I don't know if I'm doing it very well though.
